{"article_id":"bXPnklLu45BHk3pq","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"A dishy new book purports to reveal the inner secrets of the Trump White House","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"- and has already provoked President Donald Trump to a furious response .","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"The book in question is Fire and Fury : Inside the Trump White House , by longtime media writer Michael Wolff .","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"Though just released this morning ,","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"it ' s already been dominating the political news cycle for a few days .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"New York magazine published a lengthy excerpt from it Wednesday ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"the Hollywood Reporter ran a column by Wolff on the book Thursday ,","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"and the Guardian , the Washington Post , and CNBC have all run quotes from it .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"Former Trump adviser Steve Bannon , meanwhile , has come under fire from the Trump family for quotes","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"he seems to have given to Wolff .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"And the Washington Post ' s Carol Leonnig writes this morning","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"that Trump ' s lawyers have sent a cease-and-desist letter to the book ' s publisher ,","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"demanding to stop its publication .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"The excerpts from the book","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"released earlier this week","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"tell a mostly familiar big-picture story of chaos during the presidential transition and in Trump ' s early months in the White House .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"Wolff spruces things up , though , with new quotes , anecdotes , and purported personal details","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"- many of which are eye-popping and unflattering .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"Indeed , some of the things","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"Wolff describes in the excerpts","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"sound so outlandish","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"- and also happen to be so hazily sourced -","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"that there ' s already a vigorous discussion in the political world","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"about how , exactly , this book should be interpreted .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"As fact ?","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"As \" trashy tabloid fiction , \"","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"as the White House argues ?","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"Or as something in between ?","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"From what I ' ve read so far ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"my view is that we should interpret the book as a compendium of gossip","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"Wolff heard .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"A fair amount of it does clearly seem to be accurate .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"Wolff did get access to the White House","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"- reporters have seen him coming and going there this year .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"He seems to have been in the room for some of the events","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"he depicts .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"Bannon evidently talked to Wolff a great deal ,","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"and he hasn ' t disputed any of the controversial quotes","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"attributed to him","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"that have already earned him a presidential tongue lashing .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"But of course gossip is often wrong or inaccurate .","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"Sources can misstate the facts accidentally , or deliberately .","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"( A source for one of Wolff ' s anecdotes , Sam Nunberg , has previously admitted to spreading made-up Trump campaign gossip . )","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"And we don ' t really know","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"how much effort Wolff put","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"into trying to nail down whether the juicy stuff","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"we heard","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"was actually true .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Some anecdotes and details in the book don ' t seem to match known facts ;","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"others seem outright impossible to verify .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"Some people are disputing quotes","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"attributed to them .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"And Wolff is often deliberately vague about his sourcing .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"In other words , the book does seem to be a collection of stuff","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"Wolff heard .","depth":5},{"id":55,"text":"How much of that stuff is actually true is a different question","depth":5},{"id":56,"text":"- one","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"that ' s much tougher to answer .","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"Wolff is a well-connected New York columnist","depth":5},{"id":59,"text":"who ' s covered the media industry for decades .","depth":5},{"id":60,"text":"He ' s written columns for outlets like New York magazine , Vanity Fair , and the Hollywood Reporter","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"and has several books under his belt","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"( including two about wealthy media moguls ) .","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"He ' s also long been a controversial figure .","depth":4},{"id":64,"text":"For instance , in a 2004 article for the New Republic , journalist Michelle Cottle took stock of Wolff ' s work .","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"After describing his \" quick wit , dizzying writing style , and willingness","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"to say absolutely anything about anybody \"","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"in \" a catty , caustic way , \" and his fixation \" on culture , style , buzz , and money , money , money , \"","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"Cottle essentially argues","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"that Wolff is more of a gossip compiler than a rigorous reporter :","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"Much to the annoyance of Wolff 's critics , the scenes in his columns are n't recreated","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"so much as created -","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"springing from Wolff 's imagination rather than from actual knowledge of events .","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"Even Wolff acknowledges","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"that conventional reporting is n't his bag .","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"Rather , he absorbs the atmosphere and gossip","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"swirling around him at cocktail parties , on the street , and especially during those long lunches at Michael 's .","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"`` He 's around town enough","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"to have those insights ,","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"to spot people ,","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"to come across [ pieces of information ] , ''","depth":14},{"id":81,"text":"says a friend . ...","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"On a meta level , Wolff is resented for not playing by the rules of his chosen profession .","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"He has a reputation","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"for busting embargoes","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"and burning sources","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"by putting off-the-record comments on the record .","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"Wolff ' s prominence in the New York media world likely means","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"he was on Trump ' s radar for some time .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"And Trump ' s team gave him access last year -","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"Wolff got news-making interviews with Trump himself late in the primary season","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"( in which Trump struggled to answer a question about Brexit ) ,","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"and with Bannon during the transition","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"( in which the incoming White House chief strategist bragged","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"that \" darkness is good \"","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"and laid out a plan","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"to build \" an entirely new political movement \" ) .","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"So it ' s not entirely surprising that Wolff would land a great deal of access to the new White House in 2017","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"- indeed , he claims to have landed \" something like a semi-permanent seat on a couch in the West Wing \" with Trump ' s \" non-disapproval , \"","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"and to have conducted more than 200 interviews .","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"From the excerpts","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"released so far ,","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"the big-picture takeaways appear to be","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"that the White House is a chaotic mess ,","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"that many people","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"working there","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"hate each other","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"and also disdain Trump ,","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"and that Trump can be both ridiculous and mean .","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"But some more specific tidbits","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"that have drawn attention","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"are :","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"Bannon opined to Wolff","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"that Donald Trump Jr. ' s meeting with a Russian lawyer in search of dirt on Hillary Clinton was \" treasonous , \"","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"speculated the elder","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"Trump may have been involved in the meeting as well ,","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"and asserted","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"that Jared Kushner was involved in some \" greasy \" business","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"that could expose him to money laundering charges .","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"( Trump already responded to this with a furious official White House statement","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"denouncing Bannon . )","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"Katie Walsh , a deputy chief of staff","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"who lasted only about two months in Trump ' s White House ,","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"is quoted","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"that working with Trump was \" like trying to figure out what a child wants. \"","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"( Some reporters say","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"she ' s disputing the quote . )","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"One excerpt claims to describe Trump ' s methodology","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"for getting \" friends ' wives into bed , \"","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"which","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"he purportedly likes to say","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"is \" one of the things","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"that made life worth living. \"","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"( The process involves a speakerphone . )","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"Wolff makes some allusions to Trump ' s mental state :","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"\" Everybody was painfully aware of the increasing pace of his repetitions .","depth":14},{"id":137,"text":"It used to be inside of 30 minutes","depth":16},{"id":138,"text":"he ' d repeat , word-for-word and expression-for-expression , the same three stories","depth":16},{"id":139,"text":"- now it was within 10 minutes. \"","depth":15},{"id":140,"text":"( \" At Mar-a-Lago , just before the new year , a heavily made-up Trump failed to recognize a succession of old friends , \"","depth":14},{"id":141,"text":"he adds in his Hollywood Reporter column . )","depth":14},{"id":142,"text":"Another claims","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"that Trump has \" a longtime fear","depth":14},{"id":144,"text":"of being poisoned , \"","depth":14},{"id":145,"text":"which supposedly explains his love of McDonald ' s .","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"Wolff writes","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"that Mark Corallo ,","depth":15},{"id":148,"text":"who served as a spokesperson for Trump ' s legal team","depth":16},{"id":149,"text":"before resigning this summer ,","depth":16},{"id":150,"text":"privately confided","depth":14},{"id":151,"text":"that he thought","depth":14},{"id":152,"text":"an Air Force One meeting","depth":16},{"id":153,"text":"in which Trump ' s team strategized about how to respond to the news","depth":17},{"id":154,"text":"that Don Jr. had met a Russian lawyer","depth":17},{"id":155,"text":"\" represented a likely obstruction of justice . \"","depth":15},{"id":156,"text":"According to another tidbit ,","depth":12},{"id":157,"text":"when former Fox News chief Roger Ailes suggested John Boehner as a potential chief of staff for Trump during the transition ,","depth":13},{"id":158,"text":"Trump responded ,","depth":14},{"id":159,"text":"\" Who ' s that ? \"","depth":14},{"id":160,"text":"Wolff claims","depth":11},{"id":161,"text":"that Ivanka Trump made fun of her father ' s hair ,","depth":12},{"id":162,"text":"and has said to Kushner","depth":13},{"id":163,"text":"that she wants to be the first woman president .","depth":13},{"id":164,"text":"He also claims","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"that Melania Trump was in tears , \" and not of joy , \" on election night","depth":12},{"id":166,"text":"when learning","depth":13},{"id":167,"text":"Trump would win .","depth":13},{"id":168,"text":"Overall , the book ' s most eyebrow-raising claims appear to reside on a spectrum","depth":6},{"id":169,"text":"ranging at least from \" true \" to \" highly dubious gossip . \"","depth":6},{"id":170,"text":"What appears to be the biggest news in the book so far","depth":8},{"id":171,"text":"- Bannon ' s provocative speculation about the Trump family and the Russia investigation -","depth":8},{"id":172,"text":"does appear to be , at least , accurate quotation of him .","depth":7},{"id":173,"text":"Bannon isn ' t disputing any of the quotes ,","depth":8},{"id":174,"text":"and Breitbart News , the website","depth":10},{"id":175,"text":"he runs ,","depth":10},{"id":176,"text":"straightforwardly wrote them up on Wednesday .","depth":9},{"id":177,"text":"Whether Bannon ' s claims have any validity , though , isn ' t clear .","depth":7},{"id":178,"text":"Additionally , for at least some of the events","depth":7},{"id":179,"text":"Wolff describes ,","depth":7},{"id":180,"text":"he appears to have been in the room .","depth":6},{"id":181,"text":"For instance , Wolff spends a good chunk of the New York magazine excerpt","depth":7},{"id":182,"text":"describing , in detail , a dinner","depth":8},{"id":183,"text":"Bannon and Ailes shared in January .","depth":8},{"id":184,"text":"Some reporters questioned","depth":9},{"id":185,"text":"how Wolff could have written such a vivid scene ,","depth":9},{"id":186,"text":"and the passage didn ' t make his sourcing clear .","depth":8},{"id":187,"text":"But per Axios ' s Mike Allen ,","depth":8},{"id":188,"text":"Wolff was in the room ,","depth":9},{"id":189,"text":"and in fact hosted the dinner .","depth":9},{"id":190,"text":"Other tidbits are more problematic .","depth":7},{"id":191,"text":"For instance , the suggestion","depth":11},{"id":192,"text":"that Trump didn ' t know","depth":12},{"id":193,"text":"who John Boehner was in 2016","depth":12},{"id":194,"text":"appears highly dubious .","depth":10},{"id":195,"text":"Trump has tweeted about Boehner 26 times","depth":11},{"id":196,"text":"( once even mocking his occasional habit","depth":12},{"id":197,"text":"of crying )","depth":12},{"id":198,"text":"and played golf with him .","depth":10},{"id":199,"text":"It seems likely that someone told this juicy anecdote to Wolff","depth":10},{"id":200,"text":"- perhaps Ailes ,","depth":12},{"id":201,"text":"whom Wolff has covered for years ,","depth":12},{"id":202,"text":"who was the other party to the conversation ,","depth":12},{"id":203,"text":"and who died in May .","depth":12},{"id":204,"text":"But it ' s not clear","depth":10},{"id":205,"text":"whether Wolff bothered to check","depth":12},{"id":206,"text":"if it made sense ,","depth":12},{"id":207,"text":"if Trump may have momentarily misheard Ailes ' s remark ,","depth":12},{"id":208,"text":"or whether something else may have been going on .","depth":12},{"id":209,"text":"Some sourcing is also troublesome .","depth":10},{"id":210,"text":"Wolff quotes former Trump adviser Sam Nunberg purportedly describing an attempt","depth":13},{"id":211,"text":"to explain the Constitution to Trump .","depth":13},{"id":212,"text":"\" I got as far as the Fourth Amendment","depth":14},{"id":213,"text":"before his finger is pulling down on his lip","depth":15},{"id":214,"text":"and his eyes are rolling back in his head , \"","depth":15},{"id":215,"text":"Nunberg is quoted as saying .","depth":13},{"id":216,"text":"But just a few months ago , Nunberg bragged to a reporter","depth":12},{"id":217,"text":"that he made up what he said was a false story","depth":13},{"id":218,"text":"about Chris Christie getting Trump McDonald ' s during the campaign .","depth":13},{"id":219,"text":"Other sourcing , such as for the Jared and Ivanka anecdotes , is hazy .","depth":10},{"id":220,"text":"Did Wolff rigorously fact-check what he heard here ,","depth":11},{"id":221,"text":"or might it have been a bit too good to check ?","depth":11},{"id":222,"text":"Katie Walsh , meanwhile , says","depth":13},{"id":223,"text":"she ' s disputing some quotes","depth":14},{"id":224,"text":"attributed to her","depth":14},{"id":225,"text":"-","depth":12},{"id":226,"text":"but whether this is a case of factual inaccuracy on Wolff ' s part or the phenomenon","depth":13},{"id":227,"text":"known as \" source remorse \"","depth":14},{"id":228,"text":"( when someone regrets saying too much to a reporter","depth":15},{"id":229,"text":"and seeks to disavow it )","depth":15},{"id":230,"text":"isn ' t clear .","depth":12},{"id":231,"text":"( Axios ' s Allen writes this morning","depth":11},{"id":232,"text":"that Wolff taped many of his interviews ,","depth":12},{"id":233,"text":"including at least one with Walsh ,","depth":13},{"id":234,"text":"which could certainly bolster his case . )","depth":13},{"id":235,"text":"The bigger-picture issue here is that the excerpts","depth":14},{"id":236,"text":"released so far","depth":14},{"id":237,"text":"suggest","depth":13},{"id":238,"text":"Wolff used a writing style common to major reported political books - the dramatic reconstruction of scenes and sometimes dialogue in a you-are-there style ,","depth":13},{"id":239,"text":"with his specific sourcing for many claims omitted .","depth":13},{"id":240,"text":"That makes for a more entertaining read ,","depth":13},{"id":241,"text":"but it provides less transparency in the sourcing of specific claims","depth":13},{"id":242,"text":"and therefore makes it more difficult to get any sense","depth":13},{"id":243,"text":"of just how solid Wolff ' s information may be .","depth":13},{"id":244,"text":"Which scenes was he in the room for ?","depth":11},{"id":245,"text":"If he was in the room ,","depth":13},{"id":246,"text":"did he record audio","depth":15},{"id":247,"text":"and nail exact quotes ,","depth":15},{"id":248,"text":"or use some combination of notes , memory , and dramatic license ?","depth":14},{"id":249,"text":"What did he hear from sources with firsthand knowledge ?","depth":13},{"id":250,"text":"What did he hear from people with secondhand knowledge ?","depth":13},{"id":251,"text":"In the end , here ' s New York Times White House correspondent Maggie Haberman ' s assessment of the book :","depth":9},{"id":252,"text":"Thin but readable .","depth":10},{"id":253,"text":"Well written .","depth":11},{"id":254,"text":"Several things","depth":14},{"id":255,"text":"that are true","depth":14},{"id":256,"text":"and several","depth":14},{"id":257,"text":"that are not .","depth":14},{"id":258,"text":"Light in fact-checking and copy-editing .","depth":12},{"id":259,"text":"- Maggie Haberman","depth":10},{"id":260,"text":"( @ maggieNYT )","depth":10},{"id":261,"text":"January 3 , 2018","depth":9},{"id":262,"text":"Overall , my advice","depth":10},{"id":263,"text":"for reading the book","depth":10},{"id":264,"text":"is to look closely at what Wolff reveals about the sourcing of each of his claims .","depth":9},{"id":265,"text":"The most reliable stuff is , well , stuff","depth":11},{"id":266,"text":"people said on the record to Wolff directly .","depth":11},{"id":267,"text":"If the quotations directly quote people","depth":14},{"id":268,"text":"telling him things","depth":14},{"id":269,"text":"and identify them ,","depth":13},{"id":270,"text":"they are probably accurate .","depth":12},{"id":271,"text":"( That doesn ' t necessarily mean what these sources are saying is accurate ,","depth":12},{"id":272,"text":"but the quotes themselves are probably right . )","depth":12},{"id":273,"text":"Again , Bannon really does seem to have said all that stuff .","depth":9},{"id":274,"text":"Similarly , look for clues about which scenes Wolff was actually in the room for","depth":9},{"id":275,"text":"- even though , in the passages","depth":11},{"id":276,"text":"released so far ,","depth":11},{"id":277,"text":"his opaque descriptions of his sourcing can make that rather difficult .","depth":10},{"id":278,"text":"As the sourcing grows hazier ,","depth":9},{"id":279,"text":"you should probably add grains of salt accordingly .","depth":9},{"id":280,"text":"Of course , anonymity is often crucial","depth":8},{"id":281,"text":"for sources to speak candidly .","depth":8},{"id":282,"text":"But it also can allow people to spread untrue or inaccurate information .","depth":8},{"id":283,"text":"And","depth":9},{"id":284,"text":"given Wolff ' s weakness for gossip and the questions","depth":11},{"id":285,"text":"raised about some of his juicy tidbits so far ,","depth":11},{"id":286,"text":"a skeptical eye seems warranted .","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":573,"left":344,"right":572,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":344,"left":299,"right":343,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":299,"left":288,"right":298,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":288,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":298,"left":2,"right":297,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":297,"left":292,"right":296,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":292,"left":289,"right":291,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":289,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":291,"left":5,"right":290,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":290,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":296,"left":293,"right":295,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":293,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":295,"left":10,"right":294,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":294,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":343,"left":338,"right":342,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":338,"left":325,"right":337,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":325,"left":313,"right":324,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":313,"left":301,"right":312,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":301,"left":300,"right":15,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":300,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":312,"left":306,"right":311,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":306,"left":302,"right":305,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":302,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":305,"left":304,"right":21,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":304,"left":303,"right":20,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":303,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":311,"left":307,"right":310,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":307,"left":22,"right":23,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":310,"left":24,"right":309,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":309,"left":308,"right":27,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":308,"left":25,"right":26,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":324,"left":316,"right":323,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"